r-anvandas" data-discover="true"><div class="StoryGridTeaser__media___vcY6R"><div class="pic-ratio-square sm-pic-ratio-wide"><div class="pic pic--wide"><img alt="Måns Jonasson från Internetstiftelsen intervjuas i en tv-studio med stadsvy i bakgrunden." class="pic__img pic__img--optimized pic__img--wide" title="Foto: SVT" src="./Facebookbedragerier_files/92f96d0c1446a2e26c2910896a966cbf53b81c554eb655616a7792504d4eb781(1)"></div><div class="pic__ratio" style="position:absolute;visibility:hidden"></div></div><div class="PlayButton__root___fiqoS PlayButton__default-mini___nQZfd PlayButton__gteSmall-small___POmp3" aria-hidden="true"><span class="PlayButton__icon___URtGX"><svg class="" height="1em" pointer-events="none" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="1em"><use href="/static/spritesheet-ace69f59.svg#svt-icon-PlayRegular"></use></svg></span><time datetime="PT89S" class="VideoLength__root___Cvn6k VideoLength__default-mini___LtBGj VideoLength__gteSmall-small___2VHDV">1 min</time></div></div><div class="StoryGridTeaser__content___RSBFW"><h1 class="TeaserHeadline__root___nDBl0 Headline__headline-S___DoHZQ Headline__color-default___6WSmE">Experten: Drabbade något av en måltavla för bedrägerier</h1><div class="StoryGridTeaser__textContent___4xs1k"><span class="Text__text-S___iCKcf">Så kan uppgifterna användas <span aria-label="." role="img">•</span> ”Kommer låtsas vara någon du känner”</span></div></div></a></article></li><li class="StoryGrid__item___tULaU"><article class="StoryGridTeaser__root___BUeNh"><a class="StoryGridTeaser__link___Hzi4w" title="Stefan lurades av bedragarna: ”Kan hända vem som helst”" href="https://www.svt.se/nyheter/lokalt/vast/stefan-lurades-av-bedragarna-kan-handa-vem-som-helst" data-discover="true"><div class="StoryGridTeaser__media___vcY6R"><div class="pic-ratio-square sm-pic-ratio-wide"><div class="pic pic--wide"><img alt="Stefan Arff sitter i en bil och tittar ut genom fönstret en regnig dag." class="pic__img pic__img--optimized pic__img--wide" title="Foto: SVT" src="./Facebookbedragerier_files/1c9cf64140c64c65b5d59d031512021d362b28521cf823076ffe6f5198882ef6(1)"></div><div class="pic__ratio" style="position:absolute;visibility:hidden"></div></div><div class="PlayButton__root___fiqoS PlayButton__default-mini___nQZfd PlayButton__gteSmall-small___POmp3" aria-hidden="true"><span class="PlayButton__icon___URtGX"><svg class="" height="1em" pointer-events="none" role="presentation" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="1em"><use href="/static/spritesheet-ace69f59.svg#svt-icon-PlayRegular"></use></svg></span><time datetime="PT51S" class="VideoLength__root___Cvn6k VideoLength__default-mini___LtBGj VideoLength__gteSmall-small___2VHDV">51 sek</time></div></div><div class="StoryGridTeaser__content___RSBFW"><h1 class="TeaserHeadline__root___nDBl0 Headline__headline-S___DoHZQ Headline__color-default___6WSmE">Stefan lurades av bedragarna: ”Kan hända vem som helst”</h1><div class="StoryGridTeaser__textContent___4xs1k"><span class="Text__text-S___iCKcf">Liga på 14 personer döms till fängelsestraff</span></div></div></a></article></li><li class="StoryGrid__item___tULaU"><article class="StoryGridTeaser__root___BUeNh"><a class="StoryGridTeaser__link___Hzi4w" title="Bluff-sms om paket drabbar tusentals  – så känner du igen bedrägeriet" href="https://www.svt.se/nyheter/lokalt/vasternorrland/bluff-sms-om-paket-drabbar-tusentals-sa-kanner-du-igen-bedrageriet" data-discover="true"><div class="StoryGridTeaser__media___vcY6R"><div class="pic-ratio-square sm-pic-ratio-wide"><div class="pic pic--wide"><img alt="En hand håller en mobil med ett bluff-sms om paketleverans på skärmen." class="pic__img pic__img--optimized pic__img--wide" title="Foto: SVT" src="./Facebookbedragerier_files/714f58ae31601de6835a79c598611e8fc046d8dd58dfdb95fd06df6694092707"></div><div class="pic__ratio" style="position:absolute;visibility:hidden"></div></div><div class="PlayButton__root___fiqoS PlayButton__default-mini___nQZfd PlayButton__gteSmall-small___POmp3"